  "cooking_instructions": [
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Preheat the oven to 220°C/ 200°C (fan)/ gas 7 and boil a full kettle</p><p>Deseed your <strong>pepper[s] </strong>(scrape the seeds and pith out with a teaspoon) and dice</p><p>Grate your <strong>cheddar cheese</strong></p><p>Drain your<strong> sweetcorn</strong></p>",
      "order": 1,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-1-1660662489931-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-1-1660662489931-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-1-1660662489931-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-1-1660662489931-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-1-1660662489931-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>waxy potatoes</strong> to a pot of plenty of <strong>boiled water</strong> with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Once boiling, cook for 8-10 min, then drain and return to the pot with <strong>half</strong> your <strong>gochujang paste</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!) and mix it all together</p><p>Season with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong> and set aside to steam dry</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-1660662501946-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-1660662501946-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-1660662501946-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-1660662501946-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-1660662501946-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>diced pepper</strong> and <strong>grated cheese</strong> to a bowl with the <strong>chilli flakes </strong>(not a fan of spice? Just add a little!), the <strong>drained sweetcorn </strong>and <strong>half</strong> your <strong>mayo </strong>(you'll use the rest later) – this is your <strong>cheesy corn mixture</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-1660662513879-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-1660662513879-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-1660662513879-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-1660662513879-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-1660662513879-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>cheesy corn mixture</strong> to an <strong>oven-proof dish</strong></p><p>Put the dish in the oven and cook for 20 min or until the cheese has melted – this is your <strong>Korean-style cheesy corn</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-1660662524776-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-1660662524776-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-1660662524776-x700.jpg",
