          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-1660662524776-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the potatoes have steam dried, crush them lightly with a fork and then add them to a baking tray (or two!) with a small drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong></p><p>Tip: You only want the potatoes lightly crushed, not mashed!</p><p>Put the tray[s] in the oven and cook for 10-15 min or until crispy – these are your <strong>gochujang potatoes</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
